Gordini Logo Gordini is a division of Renault Sport Technologies. In the past, it was a sports car manufacturer and performance tuner, established in 1946 by Amédée Gordini, nicknamed “Le Sorcier”. Gordini became a division of Renault in 1968 and of Renault Sport in 1976. Source
